<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q37_v8" title="Q37_v8" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceC</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>
      Un estudiante quiere encontrar el número real x que hace verdadera la igualdad
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn>
      </m:math>
      y realiza el siguiente procedimiento:
      <br />
      Paso 1:
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn>
      </m:math>
      <br />
      Paso 2:
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn>
      </m:math>
      <br />
      Paso 3:
      <m:math>
        <m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn>
      </m:math>
      <br />
      Paso 4:
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
      </m:math>
      <br />
      En ¿cuál de los pasos anteriores aparece el primer error en la resolución de la ecuación?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">En el Paso 2.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. En el Paso 2 se pasa de <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn></m:math> a <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math>, lo que corresponde a restar <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> en ambos lados. Esa transformación es válida, porque <m:math><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">En el Paso 3.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El Paso 3 también es correcto, porque desde <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math>, ya que <m:math><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math>. Por lo tanto, el primer error no está en ese paso.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">En el Paso 4.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Hasta el Paso 3 se tiene <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math>. Para despejar <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>, se debe dividir ambos lados por <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, obteniendo <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>. En el Paso 4 aparece <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, pero ese <m:math><m:mn>52</m:mn></m:math> ya no corresponde, porque antes se había obtenido <m:math><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">No hay error; el procedimiento es correcto.<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Sí hay un error. Desde el Paso 3, <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math>, por lo que al dividir por <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> debe resultar <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>. El Paso 4 escribe <m:math><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>, que no coincide con la igualdad anterior.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso de la ecuación</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la ecuación original</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Restar 4 en ambos lados</strong></p>
            <p>Para aislar el término con <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>, se resta <m:math><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math> en ambos miembros:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Dividir ambos lados por 8</strong></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math> está multiplicando a <m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:math>, se divide ambos lados por <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Y como <m:math><m:mn>48</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>, resulta:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Identificar el primer error del procedimiento dado</strong></p>
            <p>Los pasos 2 y 3 del estudiante son correctos. El primer error aparece cuando escribe:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>52</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>En ese momento ya se había obtenido <m:math><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math>, así que debía usar <m:math><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:math> y no <m:math><m:mn>52</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>El primer error aparece en el <strong>Paso 4</strong>. La alternativa correcta es <strong>C</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>